Ngokombiko wesitatimende senkampani yonogada iReaction Unit South Africa (Rusa), umufi ubeyolanda imoto yomkakhe ekhalakathele emzini womsolwa kuCrocodile Road. Kuthiwa inkosikazi kamufi ibijikisa imoto yayo iHyundai i20 endleleni engenela kwayo kanti izoyiphunyuka yayokhalakathela kamakhelwane phezu kwemoto kamsolwa. Ngalesi sikhathi kuthiwa umsolwa ube esesebenzisa izimoto zakhe ezimbili evimbela imoto yenkosikazi kamufi ukuba isuswe egcekeni lakhe kuze kube kulungiswa indaba yamademeshe. “Umufi ufike ehamba ngemoto yakhe iMahindra Bolero wabe eseyalela ukuba kususwe izimoto ezivimbe imoto yomkakhe ukuze itakulwe. Kube sekuqubuka ingxabano phakathi kwabo okuphethe ngokuthi umsolwa adonse isibhamu adubule umufi esifubeni,” kusho iRusa. Kuthiwa umsolwa ubikele amaphoyisa ukuthi udubule umufi ngenhloso yokuzivikela ngoba ubefuna ukumgwaza ngommese. Kodwa kuthiwa akutholwanga mmese endaweni yesigameko. Umsolwa uboshiwe kwathathwa nesibhamu sakhe i-9mm esisemthethweni. Okhulumela amaphoyisa KwaZulu-Natal, uColonel Thembeka Mbele, usiqinisekisile lesi sigameko. UColonel Mbele uthe amaphoyisa aphenya icala lokubulala kanti umsolwa kulindeleke avele enkantolo maduze.